{"word":"G3901 - παραῤῥυέω - pararrhyéō - par-ar-hroo-eh'-o - Let slip","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραῤῥυέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pararrhyéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ar-hroo-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Let slip</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விட்டுவிலகு"},{"paragraph":"to flow past"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and the alternate of <a href=\"#/G4482 - ῥέω - rhéō - hreh'-o/4482\">G4482</a>; to <i>flow by</i>, that is, (figuratively) carelessly <i>pass</i> (<i>miss</i>): - let slip.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}